Context: Re-engaging after a period of no contact.
- Acknowledge the time elapsed naturally (no groveling)
- Reference where the conversation left off
- Provide a fresh reason to reconnect (new industry insight, relevant case study, or updated service capability)
- Keep it short: 100-150 words
- End with a low-friction ask (15-min call, quick question)`,

